Games/Lineofsight version 1.0
===============================

Line-of-sight



INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


POST-INSTALL

To get information how to use this module type the following:
   
   perldoc Games::Lineofsight.pm


